oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Muhlenberg County Fair & 4th of July Celebration
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Woodcuts (prints); Carnivals; Fairs;Holidays; Fourth of July;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Four color window card (black and red and orange on yellow and white) Hatch poster announcing the Muhlenberg County Fair and Fourth of July Celebration at the Central City Fairgrounds. Events include Gladstone Expostion shows on the midway. Poster features woodcut of circus.
